n &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12952,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/between-two-calls-to-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":34093,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Sunan prayer between Adhan and Iqamah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mughaffil reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Between every two calls to prayer is a prayer. Between every two calls to prayer is a prayer.\" Then, on the third time, the Prophet said, \"For whoever wishes.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 627, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 838 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14142,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/11\/hypocrites-if-they-knew-crawl\/","url_meta":{"origin":34093,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: They would crawl to prayer if they knew","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"No prayer is more burdensome to the hypocrites than the dawn and evening prayers. If they knew the blessing in them, they would come even if they had to crawl.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 657, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 651 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","bloc